These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: fanta, soy-milk
House: colonial, palace
2 different pets are kept: horse, hamster
2 different games are played: scrabble, bridge
1. the palace house is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3
2. the colonial house is on the right of the palace house##1
3. the person playing bridge is on the right of the owner of the horse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |
| Beverage      | soy-milk      | fanta    |
| House           | palace | colonial |
| Pet   | horse       | hamster  |
| Game     | scrabble      | bridge     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-2::.
There 2 different types of food: cauliflower, watermelon
2 different games are played: poker, canasta
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: begonia, balloon-flower
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, siglo
1. the person who growsbegonia is on the left or right of the siglo-smoker##3
2. the person eating watermelon is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
3. the siglo-smoker is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Food          | watermelon | cauliflower |
| Game   | poker       | canasta         |
| Flower           | balloon-flower     | begonia         |
| Cigar     | siglo    | davidoff    |

