.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-3::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: board-games, hiking
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: pall-mall, vegafina
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: january, february
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: baseball, ice-hockey
1. the person who's birthday is in february is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the pall-mall-smoker##1
3. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left or right of the person who's sport is baseball##3
4. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |        1        |      2      |
| Hobby         | hiking          | board-games |
| Cigar           | vegafina | pall-mall     |
| Birthday   | january            | february         |
| Sport     | ice-hockey         | baseball   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-4::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: cola, tea
The people use 2 different means of transport: motorbike, car
The people have 2 different hobbies: filmmaking, video-games
There are 2 different nationalities: spanish, nigerian
1. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left or right of the nigerian##3
2. the person drinking tea is the spanish##1
3. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person driving the car##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |
| Beverage      | tea     | cola   |
| Transport   | car    | motorbike |
| Hobby   | filmmaking   | video-games |
| Nationality           | spanish | nigerian    |

