.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-20::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: august, december
There 2 different types of food: eggplant, papaya
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, game
2 different pets are kept: snake, horse
1. the game-smoker is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
2. the person eating eggplant is the prince-smoker##1
3. the prince-smoker is the owner of the horse##1
4. the owner of the snake is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |
| Birthday      | december     | august |
| Food          | papaya   | eggplant |
| Cigar   | game     | prince     |
| Pet     | snake | horse     |

 